{
  "stem": "23498.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Many of times did I hear, you still alive?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The only good thing Hitler did that finish out the Jews, or killed the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Afterwards, I met my two cousins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Only two cousins survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Actually, three cousins.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "One was very little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- Was this after your parents came back, too?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the liberation of Praga, it still was-- the Russians were, you know, around Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- you know, the Russians called me to-- to make the-- to make the-- you know, like on the frontier, you-- you dig the ground, you know, to make [INAUDIBLE], you know, against-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] against artillery or something so you can hide.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- they called the private people, whoever was-- I couldn't-- I couldn't keep the-- the blooming thing, you  know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was so weak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, anyway, they only thing that they found my two cousins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, come over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is a Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you'll be OK over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As it came out, I wasn't OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would have been better off, you know, in the old place, because the Jewish family, they were the butchers from the same place where we used to live.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were, you know, like-- they were always envious of the rich ones.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were very poor before the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- so they had a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] in us being homeless, and so they used us very much.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they made some monkey business, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that was it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So how long did you stay with them?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With them?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not long.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my mother soon arrived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I forgot to tell you from the Slawinski.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can I go back?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A sin.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
